import { ReactComponent as WebDevelopmentIcon } from '../assets/icons/web-development-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as LandingPageIcon } from '../assets/icons/landing-page-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as SeoIcon } from '../assets/icons/seo-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as EcommerceIcon } from '../assets/icons/ecommerce-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as AdvancedLandingPageIcon } from '../assets/icons/advanced-landing-page-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as WebAppIcon } from '../assets/icons/web-app-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as SaasIcon } from '../assets/icons/saas-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as EnterpriseWebIcon } from '../assets/icons/enterprise-web-icon.svg';
import { ReactComponent as DigitalTransformationIcon } from '../assets/icons/digital-transformation-icon.svg';
import { assignRelativeBadges } from '../utils/assignRelativeBadges';

export const servicesData = [
  {
    tier: 'Freshman',
    services: assignRelativeBadges([
      {
        title: 'Starter Pack',
        description:
          'Simple 3-5 page static website with responsive design and basic contact form.',
        details: [
          'Responsive design for desktop and mobile',
          'Up to 3 custom pages',
          'Basic contact form',
          'SEO-friendly structure',
          '1 round of revisions',

        price: '$1,000',
        IconComponent: WebDevelopmentIcon,
      },
      {
        title: 'On the Come Up',
        description:
          'Single-page landing site with form capture and minimal animations.',
        details: [
          'Conversion-focused design',
          'Form integration with email capture',
          'Basic on-page SEO',
          '1 round of revisions',
        ],
        price: '$800',
        IconComponent: LandingPageIcon,
      },
      {
        title: 'Kickstart',
        description:
          'On-page SEO optimization and submission to Google Search Console.',
        details: [
          'Keyword research and implementation',
          'Meta tag creation',
          'Google Search Console submission',
          'Basic website audit report',
        ],
        price: '$500',
        IconComponent: SeoIcon,
      },
      {
        title: 'Breakthrough',
        description: 'Basic business branding and content strategy.',
        details: [
          'Logo design',
          'Basic brand guidelines',
          'Initial content strategy',
          '1 round of revisions',
        ],
        price: '$750',
        IconComponent: SeoIcon,
      },
    ]),
  },
  {
    tier: 'Prime Time',

    services: assignRelativeBadges([
      {
        title: 'Grind Mode',

          '5-10 pages with CMS integration, basic e-commerce, and SEO.',

          'Basic e-commerce functionality',
          'On-page SEO optimization',
          '3 rounds of revisions',
        ],
        price: '$4,500',
        IconComponent: EcommerceIcon,
      },

        description:
          'Optimized for conversions, integrated with CRM, and advanced animations.',

          'High-conversion design',
          'Integration with CRM (Salesforce, HubSpot)',

          'A/B testing setup',
          '3 rounds of revisions',

        price: '$3,000',
        IconComponent: AdvancedLandingPageIcon,
      },
      {
        title: 'Growth Spurt',
        description:
          'Full-stack web application with user authentication and dashboard.',
        details: [
          'Custom backend development (Node.js, Python)',
          'User authentication (OAuth, JWT)',
          'Admin and user dashboards',
          'Database integration (MongoDB, MySQL)',
          'API integrations',
        ],
        price: '$6,000',
        IconComponent: WebAppIcon,

        description: 'Advanced marketing strategy and analytics.',

          'Marketing automation setup',
          'Advanced analytics tracking',
          'Email marketing integration',
          '2 rounds of revisions',

        IconComponent: SeoIcon,

    tier: 'Mogul',
    services: assignRelativeBadges([

          'Custom SaaS platform development',

          'Brand management and guidelines',
          'Multi-channel marketing',
          'Ongoing content updates',
        ],

        IconComponent: SeoIcon,
      },
    ]),

  {
    tier: 'Legendary',
    services: assignRelativeBadges([
      {
        title: 'Hall of Fame',
        description:
          'Complete end-to-end digital transformation, including custom SaaS, web applications, and automation.',
        details: [
          'Fully integrated digital ecosystem',
          'Custom SaaS solutions',
          'Advanced AI-driven automation',
          'Enterprise-grade cloud infrastructure',
          'Dedicated support team',

        title: 'Iconic',
        description:
          'AI solutions integrated into your business processes for smarter operations.',

          'Custom AI models',
          'Process automation with AI',
          'AI-driven decision-making',
          'Ongoing model training and optimization',
          'Dedicated AI support',

        price: '$60,000+',
        IconComponent: DigitalTransformationIcon,
      },
      {
        title: 'Mastermind',
        description:
          'Leverage blockchain technology for secure, transparent, and automated operations.',

          'Custom blockchain solutions',
          'Smart contract development',
          'Secure and transparent transactions',
          'Ongoing blockchain maintenance',
          'Dedicated blockchain support team',
        ],
        price: '$75,000+',
        IconComponent: DigitalTransformationIcon,
      },
      {
        title: 'The Crown',
        description:
          'Exclusive, high-end digital experience and innovation package for industry leaders.',
        details: [
          'Personalized digital strategy',
          'Exclusive features and integrations',
          'Premium content and design',
          'Dedicated innovation team',
        ],
        price: '$100,000+',
        IconComponent: DigitalTransformationIcon,
      },

];
